                 comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3584-9998")))
Description:  This is a container package for the IIDEA shiny application, which provides an interactive volcano plot for differential gene expression analysis. By using post hoc methods, IIDEA makes it possible for users to interactively select genes of interest and obtain valid statistical guarantees regarding the number/proportion of true/false positives among these genes.
